Pacific Heights Chevron is a family owned and operated business. The Sahagun family have been small business owners for the past forty years and are very experienced in both repairs as well as customer satisfaction. It is our honor and duty to serve you with the best quality care in an efficient and timely matter.  We promise top quality parts, fair estimates, guarantee on all mechanical parts, repair services by qualified technicians, and to give the customer what they want when they want it. As your friendly helpful neighbor we are always here to support you and your vehicle’s needs, we also welcome our customer’s four legged friends. If you’re walking in the neighborhood, dropping off your car, or stopping by for gas, feel free to bring your beloved pet inside and we will gladly give them a well-deserved treat. Come visit us today we would love to serve you!